---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About · QingTools" description="Why QingTools exists and how to use it." current="about">
  <div class="about">
    <h1>About QingTools</h1>
    <p class="lead">QingTools is a box of little tools you can open in a tap — no matter who you are, whether you write code, run operations, or just need to get everyday things done.</p>

    <h2>Why we built it</h2>
    <div class="rows">
      <p><strong>Light:</strong> no login, no install — open and use.</p>
      <p><strong>Broad:</strong> from developer utilities to everyday helpers, added over time.</p>
      <p><strong>Always growing:</strong> more tools land as they are built.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>How to use it</h2>
    <p>Search from the home page or browse by category. Inside a tool, use the switcher in the top-right to jump to another tool without going back home.</p>

    <div style="border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding-top:24px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:12px;">
      <p style="color:var(--fg);margin:0;">Got a tool idea? We'd love to hear it.</p>
      <a class="btn" href="mailto:hello@qingtools.app">Suggest a tool</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
